integer n is spanned by the basis {TemplateBox[{RowBox[{\\[Lambda], ,, Y}]}, \
Ket]|Y is a standard Young tableau of shape \\[Lambda]} . We call this basis \
the Specht basis of partition \\[Lambda]. For example, consider \
\\[ScriptCapitalS]_ 3. For partition \\[Lambda]={2,1}, the Specht basis \
consists of the following two vectors, ", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {},
